FBIS3-56860 "drsov014_b_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Declines Post of Finance Minister LD2001173194 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1721 GMT 20 Jan 94 LD2001173194 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By Itar-Tass correspondent Igor Galkin] [Text] Moscow, 20 Jan -- Boris Fedorov has declined the post of Minister of Finance which had been offered to him, he said at a news conference this evening.
